```


Open Data Access
==

A basic interface to the Open Data is a available using `sondehub.download(serial=None, datetime_prefix=None)`

```
import sondehub
frames = sondehub.download(datetime_prefix="2018-10-01")
frames = sondehub.download(serial="serial")
```
